President Trump's Director of Legislative Affairs, Marc Short, has announced several additions to the Legislative Affairs Senate staff team. Amy Swonger will serve as Deputy Assistant to the President and Senate Deputy Director of Legislative Affairs. Bethany Scully will serve as Special Assistant to the President and Senate and House Special Assistant. Andy Koenig will serve as Special Assistant to the President and Policy Special Assistant. Virginia Boney and Joseph Lai will both serve as Special Assistants to the President and Senate Special Assistants. Mary Elizabeth Taylor will serve as Deputy Director of Nominations, while Cat Curry will serve as Executive Assistant to the Director of Legislative Affairs. Jim Goyer will serve as Legislative Assistant.